data.description: Look no longer if you are needing to be in the city limits, close to schools and everything else the city of Cullman has to offer.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath brick home is just what you are looking for.  Kitchen has custom made counter tops, farm sink, and new flooring so just fits the one who loves to cook and entertain. An extra bonus room provides nice area for friends and family to gather. The back yard has a 12 X 24 he/she shed and a nice privacy fence.  You don't want to miss this one.
